description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 3 of 4 of the live July match up between The Ninjas and The Pirates.
This last round is the Pirates' chance to get their first win of the year. They lost Round 2 and need to come out of the locker room strong, this team is too good to go (0-3).
The Ninjas came out in Round 2 and opened a can of whoop ass on the Pirates. The have to hold this lead and they will still be undefeated in tag team action.
Once again Vendetta controls the flow of the last round. She was dominant every second she was on the mat. Dia and Jessie had no answer for her skill or strength this night. Tara never gave in or up and limited the damage to the score. The Ninjas look like the team to beat this year!
